      "text": "Goes beyond the analysis of post-Fordist economic forms, in Robin's *Danger & opportunity* (2009), to argue that one of the four economy 'blobs' he identifies - **the mutual sector** - is far more significant than it might seem, when seen as a sphere of *cultural* as well as economic production. It produces *the labour power to remake society*. I argue there needs to be a shift *from economics to organising*."
